      "content": "that makes sense, but it feels like you're saying the \"good\" kind is just a polite way of saying the same thing. like, if people are only loyal to their own nation, doesn't that inherently make them less cooperative with the rest of the world? isn't nationalism just a precursor to conflict in the long run?",
